==評論==
===侵犯版权===
2006年3月一個關於[[數位音頻播放器|數位音頻播放器]]的網站DAPreview聲稱Engadget使用了一張原為DAPreview所拍攝的照片並裁减掉了DAPreview的標誌來占为己用<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dapreview.net/news.php?extend.3106 |title=Engadget: Busted for Unethical Blogging|accessdate=2006-11-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061006224349/http://www.dapreview.net/news.php?extend.3106 |archivedate=2006-10-06|work=Dapreview.net }}</ref>。Engadget的總編輯Ryan Block承認該照片确实曾遭複製與修剪，为此他做出了道歉并移除了这张图片<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ryanablock.com/archive/2006/03/controversy/ |title=“Controversy” |accessdate=2006-11-11 |archive-date=2007-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070310200239/http://www.ryanablock.com/archive/2006/03/controversy/ |dead-url=yes|work=Ryanablock.com }}</ref>。

